{"word":"G2641 - καταλείπω - kataleípō - kat-al-i'-po - Forsake","slug":"G2641","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<strong>Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">καταλείπω</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Transliteration: </strong>kataleípō"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Phonetic: </strong>kat-al-i'-po"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Short Definition: </strong>Forsake"},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<b>&#x03BA;&#x03B1;&#x03C4;&#x03B1;&#x03BB;&#x03B5;&#x03B9;&#x0301;&#x03C0;&#x03C9; - kataleipo&#x0304;</b> - <i>kat-al-i'-po</i><p/>From <a href=\"#/G2596\">G2596</a> and <a href=\"#/G3007\">G3007</a>; to <i>leave down</i>, that is, <i>behind</i>; by implication to <i>abandon</i>, <i>have remaining:</i> - forsake, leave, reserve."},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<strong>Cognate:</strong> <a href=\"#/G1257\">G1257</a>, <a href=\"#/G2640\">G2640</a>, <a href=\"#/G3005\">G3005</a>, <a href=\"#/G4035\">G4035</a>"}]}